<note n="0738005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0738005">偏＝遍【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0738006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0738006">根＝相【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0738007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0738007">姓＝性【三】下同</note>
